reviewText: These cartoons are phenomenal! They remind of classic Disney cartoons and others that didn't have voice acting. The animation is clean and each episode has a coherent story.

I am a huge 'Angry Birds' fan. I like the parts when the birds fight the pigs to save the eggs.
This DVD is funny and awesome!

Its crazy that this DVD is Season 3 Volume 1, I didn't even realize there were so many mini-episodes! I've only seen a few episodes before. This collection features 13 mini episodes for a total of 31 minutes.  The episodes are super short but fun to watch and short enough to watch "just one more." There are also some silly Special Features included to watch.

I received this to review in exchange for sharing my honest opinion.
